			<description><![CDATA[<p>
Nordeus is looking for talented Lead Game Designers to manage the design effort of the new and existing games. We are looking for skilled and creative people, confident in the face of new trends and ready to work on the cutting edge of the industry.</p>
<p>
<strong>What you will be doing:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Create and drive the vision for a game; communicate it within the team and throughout the company</li>
<li>
Create an overarching plan for game mechanics and economies</li>
<li>
Work with artist and designers to define the visual identity of a game</li>
<li>
Oversee and guide the design team as they define features for development</li>
<li>
Recruit new designers and mentor their career developement</li>
<li>
Remain current with industry trends (new platforms, genres, design methods)</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>What you should have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
5+ years of experience in the industry</li>
<li>
Ability to excel in a team environment and provide leadership and vision for other designers</li>
<li>
Excellent mathematical and analytical skills</li>
<li>
Strong written and verbal communications skills</li>
<li>
Experience in game balancing and system mechanics</li>
<li>
Strong knowledge of online/social game space</li>
<li>
Passionate about making and playing games</li>
</ul>
<p>
<strong>Pluses:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>
Experience in designing social games</li>
<li>
Experience in UI design</li>
<li>
Experience working in an agile project environment</li>
<li>
Computer science/software development background</li>
</ul>
<p>
If you believe you meet the requirements, please submit your up to date CV and cover letter and send them as two attachments to <a href="javascript:void(location.href='mailto:'+String.fromCharCode(106,111,98,115,64,110,111,114,100,101,117,115,46,99,111,109)+'?subject=Lead%20Game%20Designer%20-%20Application')">jobs@nordeus.eu</a>.</p>
]]></description>
